a very simple and cheap solution to make noisy garage doors quieter.";i:39;s:98:"When garage door parts are dry pushing them to work will only produce unbearable squeaking sounds.";i:40;s:70:"The following tips are sure to help you make your garage door quieter.";i:41;s:29:"Lubricate the stiff hardware.";i:42;s:69:"In most cases lubricating the metal parts is what is required of you.";i:43;s:73:"The parts you should lubricate include tracks rollers hinges and springs.";i:44;s:92:"Make sure your lubricant solution is designed to be used on metal such as 10W-30W motor oil.";}}